          <name>SENSOR_CHAN_MAX31790_FAN_FAULT</name>
          <initializer>= SENSOR_CHAN_PRIV_START</initializer>
          <briefdescription>
<para>Fan fault status bitmask. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>Each bit indicates a fault for the corresponding fan (1-6). Bit 0 = fan 1 fault, bit 1 = fan 2 fault, ..., bit 5 = fan 6 fault.</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="structsensor__value_1af21dddb084da4c42a7e77b48edf26fbe" kindref="member">sensor_value.val1</ref></computeroutput> is the 6-bit fault mask.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="structsensor__value_1a91f81bd0f5da69084cf3c629fde68a1b" kindref="member">sensor_value.val2</ref></computeroutput> is unused (always 0). </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
          </detaileddescription>
        </enumvalue>
