    <briefdescription>
<para>Maxim MAX31790 6-Channel PWM-Output Fan RPM Controller. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The MAX31790 provides fan fault monitoring and fan speed (RPM) sensing. Fan speed uses the standard <ref refid="group__sensor__interface_1ggaaa1b502bc029b10d7b23b0a25ef4e934a655a576a72cbd6641abc698a3f4304d1" kindref="member">SENSOR_CHAN_RPM</ref> channel. </para>
